{"tid":1999861,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"巴菲特：無膽不要買股票！","createTime":"2020-05-03T12:47:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-03T17:29:33.000Z","uid":4740,"like":26,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"abb38b6fecc02516433e85984c3e40f050de47c2","tid":1999861,"uid":4740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T12:47:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gii48ix.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGii48ix.jpg&h=21b5284e&s={SIZE}\" />  <br />\n <br />\n有投資者問道現在買股票是否不安全，否則為甚麼巴郡手持大量現金而不作投資。巴菲特指出，若以最差的情況去作預算，例如2008和09年期間，目前手持的現金並非很大量。他重申，買股票並持有20至30年，將會有理想回報，但若是短炒、以至以兩年投資期來說，也不知道是不是一個好時機。<br />\n<br />\n他指出，任何人在買股票時，都應該在財政上和心理上能夠應付長時間持貨的情況。沒有人能輕易撈底，要在股價再下跌五成或更多時，仍然覺得安樂，才可以買。他自己在兩年前就曾分享過，在歷史上，巴郡股價曾三次大跌超過五成，但那不是巴郡的問題，而若果你買的錢是借來的，那你隨時已被清倉了。<br />\n<br />\n他對投資者的另一個建議是，在投資時不要靠其他人，要靠自己做最適合自己的投資決定。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/buffett-berkshire-shouldnt-own-stocks-cant-handle-fear-063259125.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2Fbuffett-berkshire-shouldnt-own-stocks-cant-handle-fear-063259125.html&d=5G%2Bx0n%2BFJXS0hP%2BJIuhjglUwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=741e9af5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/buffett-berkshire-shouldnt-own-stocks-cant-handle-fear-063259125.html</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37e78859ccdc869c5e95535e29af7ebe503716e9","tid":1999861,"uid":258578,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T12:48:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3efd12c3095fb1c309c7084dcb36afad3f2cc677","tid":1999861,"uid":211062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T12:49:19.000Z","msg":"Rip"},{"pid":"c0a1175e7ab4b1f382298045a7a162d492280f00","tid":1999861,"uid":31389,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T12:50:59.000Z","msg":"失敗者買股票 成功者買牛熊"},{"pid":"234d28339c625baec742bc4135bf0c4a8